comments.body:
@rhatdan Thanks for the answer Dan. Please is there any alternative to the VSF driver?  the fuse-overlay is not available for SLES 12, this is the only OS I would use for now.
Sorry if a silly question, I'm new using Podman.

Thanks!

@vrothberg Valentin, thank you too for your attention and help!

Please, is there any recommended documentation about  _how to setup rootless Podman storage driver to overlayfs_ ?

Thanks folks!

@RodGaiotto, to the best of my knowledge there is no tutorial for that.

The [storage.conf man page](https://github.com/containers/storage/blob/main/docs/containers-storage.conf.5.md) is the best shot for docs.

But Podman should be smart enough to default to using `overlay` if the kernel supports rootless overlay fs or when fuse-overlayfs is installed.
